<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>Courses · jonnify</title>
<meta name="description" content="jonnify courses — two in-depth, English-language courses built on the jonnify design system: Functional Programming in Elixir on the BEAM, and the Agile Agent Workflow for shipping reliable software with Claude agents.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,500;1,600&family=PT+Serif:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href={~p"/assets/courses.css"}>
</head>

<body data-level="basic">
<div class="topbar"><div class="topbar-inner">
  <a href="/" class="brand"><span class="brand-mark"></span><span>jonnify · courses</span></a>
  <span class="route-tag">/courses</span>
</div></div>
<section class="hero hub-hero" id="top"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow"><span class="line"></span><span class="smallcaps">jonnify · courses</span></div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">In-depth <em>courses</em><span style="color:var(--gold)">.</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Two English-language courses built on the jonnify design system: functional programming on the BEAM, and an agile workflow for shipping reliable software with Claude agents. Each is a deep, hands-on dive with interactive elements.</p>
</div></section>
<section id="series"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="section-mark"><span class="num">courses</span><span class="lbl">2 deep dives</span></div>
  <h2 style="margin-bottom:6px">Choose a course</h2>
  <p style="color:var(--cream-soft);margin:0 0 22px">Both are taught in English and open in any order. Filter by track below.</p>
  <div class="filter-bar" role="group" aria-label="Filter courses by track">
    <button type="button" class="filter-btn active" data-tag="all" aria-pressed="true">All<span class="cnt">2</span></button>
    <button type="button" class="filter-btn" data-tag="elixir" aria-pressed="false">Elixir<span class="cnt">1</span></button>
    <button type="button" class="filter-btn" data-tag="agents" aria-pressed="false">Agents<span class="cnt">1</span></button>
  </div>
  <div class="series-grid">
    <a class="series-card" data-tags="elixir" href="/elixir" style="--accent:var(--gold-bright)">
      <div class="s-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M13 35 L24 9 M21 22 L31 35"/><circle cx="22" cy="22" r="18" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-opacity="0.5"/></svg></div>
      <div class="s-eyebrow">Elixir · BEAM · English</div>
      <h3>Functional Programming</h3>
      <p>A deep dive into functional programming with Elixir on the BEAM — from foundational to advanced computer-science problems, with interactive elements.</p>
      <div class="s-go">Open →</div>
    </a>
    <a class="series-card" data-tags="agents" href="/course/agile-agent-workflow" style="--accent:#cdb8f0">
      <div class="s-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="3.4"/><circle cx="11" cy="33" r="3.4"/><circle cx="33" cy="22" r="3.4"/><path d="M11 14.4 L11 29.6 M14 11 L22 11 Q30 11 30.6 19 M14 33 L22 33 Q30 33 30.6 25"/><path d="M29.5 22.5 L32 25 L37 18.5"/></svg></div>
      <div class="s-eyebrow">Claude Agents · Portal · English</div>
      <h3>Agile Agent Workflow</h3>
      <p>Pragmatic Programming with Claude Agents — decompose into user stories, plan a roadmap, write the spec and agent brief, and prove each increment correct, built end to end on the Portal.</p>
      <div class="s-go">Open →</div>
    </a>
  </div>
</div></section>
<footer><div class="foot-mark"><svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="14"/><path d="M20 6 L20 34 M6 20 L34 20"/></svg></div>
<p>jonnify courses — functional programming in Elixir, and the agile agent workflow for building software with Claude agents.</p><p style="color:var(--muted-2);font-size:.82rem">(с) jonnify</p></footer>
<script src={~p"/assets/courses.js"}></script>
</body></html>
